    "This benchmark is composed of clinical vignettes accompanied by four answer choices, with only one correct answer 26.",
    "We modified the MedQA-USMLE benchmark in three steps to create MetaMedQA as shown in Fig. 1: 1.",
    "Inclusion of Fictional Questions: To test the models' capabilities in recognizing their knowledge gaps, we included 100 questions from the Glianorex benchmark 27, which is constructed in the format of MedQA-USMLE but pertains to a fictional organ.",
